messages.messageBody:
Shane is a pretty much thrilled his interview got so much attention.
He is going to try and get an interview from the other side but my
husband doesn't think the studios will talk to him. I think he's
planning on walking the picket line with the strikers tomorrow
morning.

Someone on livejournal called him an "alleged 15 year old" I guess
that was meant as a complement ...

Lauren

A 15 year old unschooler (who has a parent on this list who who may
remain anonymous if so desired) interviewed the head writer for The
Tonight Show about the strike. Lots of people have commented on it
here:
http://stranahan.com/2007/11/10/writers-strike-interview-with-joe-
medeiros/

and it has made the news here:

http://www.deadlinehollywooddaily.com/tonight-shows-head-writer-
speaks-out/

Great story!

Sandra
